# Nested libgit2-backed CAS / runtime-repo stores inside evidence dirs.
# Each problem run writes a self-contained git repo at cas/, runtime_repo/,
# cas_runtime_repo/, tamper/, tamper2/ — these are content-addressed stores
# with their own .git/ and the parent repo cannot embed them as plain files
# without packing .git -> _dotgit_post_tar (the older pre-2026-05-07 convention).
# Tracked outside-the-store artifacts (run_manifest, evaluator.{stderr,stdout},
# h_vppu_history.json, verdict.json, chain_invariant.json) capture the run for
# replay. Older evidence runs that DID pack their inner .git remain tracked.
handover/evidence/**/cas/
handover/evidence/**/runtime_repo/
handover/evidence/**/cas_runtime_repo/
handover/evidence/**/tamper/
handover/evidence/**/tamper2/

# W4.3: Phase 7 §6a verifier workspace scratch dir (setup/teardown scripts)
tmp/
